_sText:
If this map is very bright for you, disable high dynamic range.

Main map - 5 min seg, 10+ min casually

Bonus - 20 sec~

This is a map I have been working on for quite some time. Originally, parts of the stages were meant to be for the bhop 2020 tournament but I realised I didn't have time to detail it to the extent i wanted to, so I decided to just go all out on what will be my final bhop map (besides maybe a few collabs or something here and there)  This map consists of 8 stages with completely varied gameplay. The difficulty goes up each stage, kinda like Sqee.  Never really used hdr before and it seems a bit weird on this map but nobody complained whilst testing so hopefully none of you find it an issue either. I really did try to make this map something totally different from what I usually upload and I hope y'all like it.

Thanks, and have fun!
